@kong_base_url = http://localhost:18000
@search_service_base_url = http://localhost:8084
@keyword = Laptop
@invalid_token = invalid.jwt.token

### Health - direct service
GET {{search_service_base_url}}/actuator/health

### Search tenant-scoped master data as tenant1 through Kong
GET {{kong_base_url}}/api/search/master-data?keyword={{keyword}}
Authorization: Bearer {{tenant1_token}}
X-Request-Id: search-tenant1-001

### Search tenant-scoped master data as tenant2 through Kong
GET {{kong_base_url}}/api/search/master-data?keyword={{keyword}}
Authorization: Bearer {{tenant2_token}}
X-Request-Id: search-tenant2-001

### Missing token should return 401
GET {{kong_base_url}}/api/search/master-data?keyword={{keyword}}
X-Request-Id: search-missing-token-001

### Invalid token should return 401
GET {{kong_base_url}}/api/search/master-data?keyword={{keyword}}
Authorization: Bearer {{invalid_token}}
X-Request-Id: search-invalid-token-001

### Blank keyword should return 400 after authentication
GET {{kong_base_url}}/api/search/master-data?keyword=
Authorization: Bearer {{tenant1_token}}
X-Request-Id: search-blank-keyword-001

### Reindex missing token - expected 401
POST {{kong_base_url}}/api/search/master-data/reindex
X-Request-Id: search-reindex-missing-token-001

### Reindex as ACCOUNTANT - expected 403
POST {{kong_base_url}}/api/search/master-data/reindex
Authorization: Bearer {{tenant1_token}}
X-Request-Id: search-reindex-accountant-403

### Reindex as VIEWER - expected 403
POST {{kong_base_url}}/api/search/master-data/reindex
Authorization: Bearer {{tenant2_token}}
X-Request-Id: search-reindex-viewer-403

### Reindex as platform admin - expected 200
POST {{kong_base_url}}/api/search/master-data/reindex
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
X-Request-Id: search-reindex-admin-001

### Search after reindex
GET {{kong_base_url}}/api/search/master-data?keyword={{keyword}}
Authorization: Bearer {{admin_token}}
X-Request-Id: search-after-reindex-001
